00:04:45.530 --> 00:04:48.160
from the School of the
Arts and Architecture,

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:50.510
and two members from the wider faculties

00:04:50.510 --> 00:04:52.650
across all of the other schools,

00:04:52.650 --> 00:04:54.800
