or functional structures

00:25:43.425 --> 00:25:44.810
from the bottom up?

00:25:44.810 --> 00:25:47.420
Can we make bigger and bigger precise,

00:25:47.420 --> 00:25:50.240
or sufficiently precise
structures to understand

00:25:50.240 --> 00:25:51.880
and control their properties,

00:25:51.880 --> 00:25:54.340
or, for instance, to
interact with the brain?

00:25:54.340 --> 00:25:56.950
The scale of biology is the nanoscale,

00:25:56.950 --> 00:25:58.940
and so we have this opportunity

00:25:58.940 --> 00:26:01.783
