01:09:22.963 --> 01:09:26.300
which we hope will be built in Hawaii,

01:09:26.300 --> 01:09:28.020
and it's a collaboration between

01:09:28.020 --> 01:09:32.352
the University of
California, Caltech, Canada,

01:09:32.352 --> 01:09:34.870
Japan, China, and India.

01:09:34.870 --> 01:09:38.421
So that brings is into
other connections of space,

01:09:38.421 --> 01:09:39.890
and connectivity in the world

01:09:39.890 --> 01:09:42.500
that brings us back to a human scale.

01:09:42.500 --> 01:09:44.056
