01:12:37.040 --> 01:12:38.530
- Yeah.

01:12:38.530 --> 01:12:40.550
- In working with these
very large telescopes,

01:12:40.550 --> 01:12:42.460
because it's a huge investment

01:12:42.460 --> 01:12:46.763
so you have to share that tool.

01:12:48.600 --> 01:12:51.660
Another connection though
