01:13:06.940 --> 01:13:09.070
these orbits that are in three dimensions,

01:13:09.070 --> 01:13:10.980
and see them from different perspectives,

01:13:10.980 --> 01:13:12.280
because of course in two dimensions

01:13:12.280 --> 01:13:14.240
you have a very different understanding

01:13:14.240 --> 01:13:15.970
about the space between objects,

01:13:15.970 --> 01:13:19.030
which is enormous, but
they seem to overlap

01:13:19.030 --> 01:13:20.980
when you only look at it in projection.

01:13:22.260 --> 01:13:25.073
- Most of our time is spent
