Like in my space, I have white walls,

01:15:15.090 --> 01:15:17.863
and the only conditions
of the world I make there

01:15:17.863 --> 01:15:21.803
is that you need to be
able to leave the room.

01:15:21.803 --> 01:15:23.410
That's like, that is the
only condition of the world

01:15:23.410 --> 01:15:25.250
to be made inside the
studio that at some point

01:15:25.250 --> 01:15:27.110
I have to get it through the door.

01:15:27.110 --> 01:15:30.622
And that is like the only
scale that is important.

01:15:30.622 --> 01:15:32.329
(audience laughing)

01:15:32.329 --> 01:15:33.670
So all the things that happen there,

01:15:33.670 --> 01:15:36.040
and all the potential of the buildings,

01:15:36.040 --> 01:15:39.014
the materials that I use,
I use a lot of clay...

01:15:39.014 --> 01:15:41.810
I'm a photographer but I use
clay, I use wood, I use metal,

01:15:41.810 --> 01:15:43.600
and as you saw I use graphite,

01:15:43.600 --> 01:15:45.930
I use all the materials that they are made

01:15:45.930 --> 01:15:49.513
for other situations that are
not necessarily art sometimes.

01:15:50.838 --> 01:15:55.176
So it's interesting thinking
about how everything start

01:15:55.176 --> 01:15:58.143
in art in a more unfinished way,

01:15:59.980 --> 01:16:03.950
and you surrendered yourself
with cultural gravitas

01:16:03.950 --> 01:16:06.540
or material memory,

01:16:06.540 --> 01:16:10.000
things like that that will
make a work of art work,

01:16:10.000 --> 01:16:13.070
like be performing as a cultural object.

01:16:13.070 --> 01:16:14.990
Now, I'm interested in this, I mean,

01:16:14.990 --> 01:16:18.430
thinking about low income
housing, or you know those idea,

01:16:18.430 --> 01:16:20.570
they have a house project in Chile,

01:16:20.570 --> 01:16:24.590
the Chilean architect
that makes the houses

01:16:24.590 --> 01:16:28.080
after the earthquake, he gives half house.

01:16:28.080 --> 01:16:29.000
- [Dina] It's Aravena.

01:16:29.000 --> 01:16:31.530
- Yeah, like Aravena, yeah, right.

01:16:31.530 --> 01:16:33.570
And it's like something
that people can finish,

01:16:33.570 --> 01:16:35.720
you know, it's like
something that people can go

01:16:35.720 --> 01:16:37.660
