to customize their house,

01:16:37.660 --> 01:16:41.010
so you build it enough to
make a cheap but sustainable,

01:16:41.010 --> 01:16:42.400
and then you can just,

01:16:42.400 --> 01:16:44.460
as you make money through your lifetime,

01:16:44.460 --> 01:16:46.170
you can customize it and fix it.

01:16:46.170 --> 01:16:47.443
And it's a really interesting project,

01:16:47.443 --> 01:16:48.276
that you could just look at it,

01:16:48.276 --> 01:16:51.250
it's like, some of them not
