01:16:51.250 --> 01:16:53.510
You know, it's like,
and when they are empty

01:16:53.510 --> 01:16:55.220
they are full of potential.

01:16:55.220 --> 01:16:57.090
So I like that about this point,

01:16:57.090 --> 01:17:02.090
but it's a place where they
have more potential than beauty,

01:17:02.098 --> 01:17:05.290
and that is usually an
