01:19:45.540 --> 01:19:49.030
So as a result, you see a
lot of astronomers who are

01:19:49.030 --> 01:19:51.871
incredibly committed to this
public engagement piece.

01:19:51.871 --> 01:19:53.729
- [Brett] Yeah.

01:19:53.729 --> 01:19:55.650
- So I engage in a lot of this

01:19:55.650 --> 01:19:58.010
not only because I think it's important,

